description: Try our easy to follow Healthier Omelette With Greens recipe. Absolutely delicious with the best ingredients from Woolworths.
keywords: Omelette,Pescatarian,Seafood free,Tree nut free,Egg,Healthier Easier,Spring,Video,Low sugar,High protein,High fibre,Quick & easy lunch,Spinach,Peanut free
name: Healthier Omelette With Greens Recipe | Woolworths

recipeInstructions.text: Whisk eggs in a bowl. Add cheese and stir to combine.
Heat half the oil in a 26cm frying pan over medium-low heat. Add half the egg mixture and cook for 3 minutes or until just set but still a little runny on top.

Lightly season with pepper, then top with half each of the peas, spinach and dill over one side of omelette. Cook for a further 1 minute. Gently fold over filling, then transfer to a plate. Repeat to make a total of 2 omelettes.
